        <p class="note"><b class="Bold">BEST PRACTICES NOTE:</b> To avoid potential issues if a carrier changes their name, avoid using FLI_ORGANIZATION_NAME or FLI_PRODUCT_CARRIER_NAME in rules. Use FLI_ORGANIZATION_ID instead of FLI_ORGANIZATION_NAME and use FLI_PRODUCT_CARRIER_ID instead of FLI_PRODUCT_CARRIER_NAME, because the IDs would not change with a rebrand. </p>
